15
00:01:01,617 --> 00:01:03,721
[Episode 6]

16
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:10,080
That boy got himself
into a heap of debt,

17
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:12,520
so he had no choice
but to sell the house.

18
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,560
I'm sorry about that.

19
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:15,760
I'll transfer the remaining rent

20
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,520
to you as soon as I can.

21
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:22,280
The only one
who can cough up three million

22
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:24,440
[Yu]
on the spot is Bai Qingyu.

23
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:30,240
The number you dialed
is currently switched off.

24
00:01:34,682 --> 00:01:37,682
[Bai Qingyu, this is Xu Wei. Can you
lend me some money? It's urgent.]

25
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,320
Why isn't Bai Qingyu back yet?

26
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:54,160
The number you dialed
is currently switched off.

27
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,840
His phone is still off.

28
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,920
What's wrong?

29
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,120
Dad,

30
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:14,880
I need to borrow some money.

31
00:02:17,085 --> 00:02:18,172
[Cheque]

32
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,280
What are you doing in my room?

33
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,800
What is this?

34
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:38,440
Give it back.

35
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,600
Is this the reason

36
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,040
you came to the Bai family?

37
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,760
You pretended you didn't care.

38
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:45,680
Now,

39
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,200
bit by bit,

40
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,680
you're showing your true colours.

41
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,680
Do you know what people

42
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,920
are saying about you?

43
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,160
Shut up.

44
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,160
Do women like you

45
00:02:58,720 --> 00:02:59,520
do anything

46
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,760
for money?

47
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,600
Didn't you join the Bai family
for money?

48
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,840
I can give it to you too.

49
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,000
Fine.

50
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,480
Tell me how much you can give me.

51
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:15,920
See if you can satisfy me.

52
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,960
Your greed is insatiable.

53
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:19,960
The kind of person I am

54
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,480
is none of your business.

55
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,040
I'm warning you.

56
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,160
Get out of the Bai family right now.

57
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:29,480
Stop it!

58
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,760
You bastard!

59
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,880
She's your sister!

60
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,520
This is her home too.

61
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:37,920
Sister?

62
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:39,640
She's no sister of mine.

63
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:40,840
You...

64
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:43,960
Yu!

65
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:46,760
Wei,

66
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,600
what's going on?

67
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,640
Wei,

68
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,080
stay away

69
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,760
from that bastard from now on.

70
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,160
If he bullies you again,

71
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,400
I'll break his legs.

72
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,520
Bai Qingyu,

73
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:08,240
this is Xu Wei.

74
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:10,120
Can you lend me some money?

75
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,040
It's urgent.

76
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:12,680
Yu.

77
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:17,759
Madam Yun.

78
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,280
Yu.

79
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,440
You've misunderstood Wei.

80
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,840
She borrowed that three million

81
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,240
from your father.

82
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:28,800
Why does she need the money?

83
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,640
They're selling off the house
she and her family used to live in.

84
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,880
You know she lost her parents
when she was young.

85
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,240
That house holds

86
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,440
all the precious memories

87
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,960
she has of them.

88
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,880
She wants to buy it to hold on

89
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,480
to those memories.

90
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,320
I know you set someone up to attack me.

91
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,600
You cut me off from my fortune.

92
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,760
I haven't settled that score
with you yet,

93
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,000
and you dare throw water on me?

94
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:08,640
Zhao Yibin,

95
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:11,360
here's a way for you to strike it rich.

96
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,000
Want to hear it?

97
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:19,680
What is it?

98
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,800
Over the years,
you've been reaping the benefits

99
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,520
from the Bai family under the pretense
of looking after your uncle.

100
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,080
Have you been investigating me?

101
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:30,800
You know your role in the car accident

102
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:32,640
between the Bai and Xu families.

103
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:37,440
I haven't done anything.
I had nothing to do with that accident.

104
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,680
Tell me the truth,

105
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:43,400
and not only will I
not hold you responsible,

106
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,160
but I'll even give you
a hefty sum of money.

107
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,680
Why did he come looking for you again?

108
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,080
Xu Wei,

109
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,200
what's wrong?

110
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,320
You have a fever.

111
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,120
Come on.

112
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,080
Let's go.

113
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:14,640
You're awake.

114
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:16,640
Feeling better?

115
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:22,160
How could you go
to a place like that alone?

116
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,520
Do you know how dangerous it is

117
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:26,280
to deal with someone like Zhao Yibin?

118
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,320
Can you tell me why

119
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:31,040
you went to see Zhao Yibin today?

120
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,520
If you don't want to talk about it,

121
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:37,840
I'll stop asking.

122
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,400
About the cheque,

123
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,680
I misunderstood you.

124
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,520
I apologise.

125
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,200
I accept your apology.

126
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,440
Daddy...

127
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:08,760
Mommy...

128
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,800
What's wrong, Wei?

129
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,520
Did you have a nightmare?

130
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,280
Does it hurt somewhere?

131
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,280
Madam Yun...

132
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:24,920
I'm fine.

133
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,160
I'll get you some water.

134
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:29,240
Oh, you.

135
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,760
You were running a high fever.
You should've been resting

136
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,440
instead of working on
some business deal.

137
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,360
I was discussing business.

138
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:42,600
Luckily, Yu was there yesterday.

139
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,360
Otherwise, what would we do

140
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,240
if something happened?

141
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,200
Where...

142
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:49,680
Where is he?

143
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,640
Yu?

144
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,400
Wei,

145
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,120
no matter what,

146
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,640
you and Yu are family now.

147
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:01,680
You're his older sister.

148
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,760
If Yu does anything out of line,

149
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,000
you must tell me and your father.

150
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:14,880
Dr. Bai,

151
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:15,840
this is Tuan's receipt.

152
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,080
Tuan, look.

153
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,320
I brought you your favourite lollipop.

154
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,920
Daddy Bai!

155
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:28,960
Tuan.

156
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:33,000
Daddy Bai, I miss Mommy Xu.

157
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,919
Mommy Xu is sick.

158
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,439
She'll come and see you
in a few days, all right?

159
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,560
Wei is sick?

160
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,240
What happened?

161
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,559
How is that any of your concern?

162
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,080
If it were me,

163
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,000
I would take better care of her.

164
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,960
Well, you lost your chance.

165
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,080
Daddy Bai, I want to go back.

166
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,320
All right. Let's go.

167
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:58,080
Is she taking her medicine and shots?

168
00:08:58,880 --> 00:08:59,640
Yes.

169
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:02,680
Daddy Bai, take good care of her.

170
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:05,400
Tuan, you have to take care
of yourself too.

171
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:06,440
Understand?

172
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,600
This is a good opportunity.

173
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,240
Madam Yun?

174
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,280
Madam Yun?

175
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,560
The shower head in my room is broken.

176
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:22,880
If Madam Yun finds out,
she won't stop nagging about me

177
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,280
taking a shower while being sick.

178
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:27,000
Bai Qingyu should be
at the hospital right now.

179
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:28,960
I'll borrow his bathroom for a bit.

180
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:41,320
Get out.

181
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,680
I think

182
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:45,600
this is my room.

183
00:09:53,477 --> 00:09:57,981
♪Hidden clouds,
dim light falling on the back♪

184
00:09:59,372 --> 00:10:07,101
♪The solitary bench at the street corner
shelters emotions♪

185
00:10:09,341 --> 00:10:12,901
♪The moon's trajectory in the night sky♪

186
00:10:13,461 --> 00:10:16,982
♪Is mending my sad heart♪

187
00:10:17,302 --> 00:10:19,781
♪My courage to get close to you♪

188
00:10:20,231 --> 00:10:23,438
♪Stops me from running away♪

189
00:10:24,621 --> 00:10:26,541
♪The wheel of fate is turning,
and we meet again♪

190
00:10:26,832 --> 00:10:28,285
♪Piecing our memories desperately♪

191
00:10:28,741 --> 00:10:30,981
♪Love takes us by surprise♪

192
00:10:31,781 --> 00:10:33,501
♪The you in the photo album♪

193
00:10:33,941 --> 00:10:38,101
♪Are shining in the past like stars♪

194
00:10:39,516 --> 00:10:42,621
♪You are in the light and shadow♪

195
00:10:43,301 --> 00:10:46,781
♪Melting all my fear away♪

196
00:10:47,141 --> 00:10:50,635
♪Those youthful memories
are healing enough♪

197
00:10:51,085 --> 00:10:54,901
♪That I become obsessed with them♪

198
00:10:55,301 --> 00:10:58,781
♪The world is suddenly full of meanings♪

199
00:10:59,358 --> 00:11:02,981
♪Walking through the rain,
I have found you♪

200
00:11:03,981 --> 00:11:05,621
♪In between the embrace♪

201
00:11:05,981 --> 00:11:08,901
♪Are the stars
scattered across the horizon♪
